ğŸ§  For Demonstration
-------------------------------------------------------------

Data generation mode can be switched using an environment variable:

environment:
  - USE_SIMULATED=true

When you get real sensors (ESP32 or others), you can replace `simulated_data.py` with `sensor_input.py`.

